    "description": "The CFD model used for hemolysis prediction shall satisfy credibility factors at levels commensurate with Model Risk Level 2 as defined in ASME V&V 40-2018. Acceptance criterion for relative hemolysis index: RH < 1.0 compared to predicate device. Numerical uncertainty shall be quantified per Richardson extrapolation procedures specified in ASME V&V 40-2018 Section 5.3.",
